    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that youre not a doctor but i'm just looking for some general info. i've been reading online that if your diet is super consistent and you feel really good, you usually dont need the full dose anymore. like, is there a standard way people taper down? i just dont want to be taking more than my body actually needs if i'm already doing everything right.",
